g on all levels (United States).png|thumb|right|Federal, state, and local government spending as a % of GDP history]]\n[[File:Revenue and Expense to GDP Chart 1993 - 2012.png|thumb|left|Revenue and Expense as % GDP.]]\n{{clear}}\n\n===Debt===\n{{Main|United States public debt}}\n[[File:US-assets.jpg|thumb|left|[[Asset]]s of the United States as a fraction of [[Gross domestic product|GDP]] 1960\u20132008]]\n[[File:US-liabilities.jpg|thumb|[[Liability (accounting)|Liabilities]] of the United States as a fraction of [[Gross domestic product|GDP]] 1960\u20132009]]\n[[File:US federal government debt ceiling from 1990 to 2013.png|thumb|left|Development of US federal [[United States debt ceiling|government debt ceiling]] from 1990 to January 2012.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whitehouse.gov/omb/budget/historicals|title=Table 7.3 \u2013 Statutory Limits on Federal Debt: 1940\u2013Current|publisher= [[Office of Management and Budget]]|accessdate=December 25, 2013}}</ref>]]\n[[File:U.S. Total Deficits vs. National Debt Increases 2001-2010.png|thumb|Deficit and debt increases 2001\u20132016.]]\n[[File:USDebt.png|thumb|left|U.S. public net debt and the total public debt]]\n{{clear}}\n\n===Deficit===\n[[File:Annual Federal Deficit as a percent of GDP.pdf|thumb|right|350px|Annual federal deficit as a percent of GDP]]\n[[File:TwinE.PNG|thumb|left|350px|\"Twin deficit\" (1960\u20132006)]]\n{{clear}}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Credit in the Thirteen Colonies]]\n* [[History of agriculture in the United States]]\n* [[History of banking in the United States]]\n* [[History of coal mining in the United States]]\n* [[List of regions by past GDP (PPP)]]\n* [[Productivity improving technologies (historical)]]\n* [[Wall Street#History|Wall Street's history]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|22em}}\n\n==Bibliography==\n* Browning, Andrew H. ''The Panic of 1819: The First Great Depression'' (2019) Comprehensive scholarly history of the era in the United States; [https://www.amazon.com/Panic-1819-Depres